      "field": "['after_hours_flow_summary']",
      "type": "updated",
      "old_value": "Clara answers every call, determines if it's an emergency, and routes accordingly. Emergencies are transferred to Marcus or Jesse. Non-emergencies are documented for morning follow-up.",
      "new_value": "After hours, Clara answers calls and determines if it's an emergency. Emergency calls are transferred to Marcus first, then Jesse, with a 20-minute callback promise. Non-emergency calls have messages taken and are promised a callback by 8 AM the next business day or 7 AM Monday for weekend calls. All after-hours non-emergency details are emailed to Tony and Marcus.",
