      "old_value": "Clara answers every call, qualifies the call, gathers information, and routes it to the appropriate person. Emergencies get transferred live. Non-emergencies get documented and sent to the team.",
      "new_value": "During business hours, Clara answers calls and routes them based on the type of inquiry. Emergency calls are transferred first to Tony, then Marcus, with a 10-minute callback promise. Service calls and water heater inquiries are sent to Tony and Marcus. Repiping, trenchless sewer, and remodel leads are sent to Marcus with a text notification. Billing inquiries go to Lori and Tony. VIP commercial clients receive immediate live transfer attempts to Tony then Marcus.",
      "reason": "Updated during onboarding"
